    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to not-assessed status consistent with MRL 2 requirements. Validation evidence demonstrates RH index prediction within 4.2% of experimental measurements across the CPB operating envelope. The CFD model is judged credible for the intended use of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RH < 1 criterion satisfied at all evaluated operating points. Assessment accepted for regulatory submission.",
